OL,3,GNorth East
OL,4,
OL,5,CThis Evening and Tonight:FLow cloud
OL,6,Fdevelops over the North Sea and is
OL,7,Fexpected to spread inland to cover
OL,8,Fmost of the region by the morning.
OL,9,FLight northeasterly wind, breezy along
OL,10,Fthe coast.
OL,11,
OL,12,CMonday:FLow cloud will burn back to
OL,13,Fthe coast during the morning to give
OL,14,Fsunny spells for most places inland.
OL,15,FTemperatures around or a little above
OL,16,Faverage. Breezy northeasterly winds.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
